
Event Planning App - Requirements

âœ… Functional Requirements

1. User Management
- User registration/login (email, social media)
- User profiles (organizer/attendee)
- Role-based permissions

2. Event Creation & Management
- Create, edit, and delete events
- Set event details: name, date, time, location, type
- Upload media (images, flyers)
- Add agenda/schedule
- Recurring events support

3. Invitations & RSVPs
- Send invitations (via email, SMS, in-app)
- RSVP tracking
- Waitlist support
- Add guests manually or via contact import

4. Calendar & Scheduling
- Event calendar view
- Time zone support
- Reminders and push notifications

5. Location Integration
- Map integration (Google Maps, Mapbox)
- Venue suggestions
- Directions for attendees

6. Collaboration Tools
- Shared planning (invite co-hosts)
- Task assignment and checklist
- In-app chat or comments

7. Ticketing & Payments
- Ticket creation (free/paid)
- Payment integration (Stripe, PayPal)
- QR code generation for check-in
- Refund handling

8. Attendee Engagement
- Live polls or Q&A
- Comments or forums
- Announcements or updates

9. Notifications
- Push and/or email notifications
- Event reminders
- Real-time updates (e.g., cancellations, venue changes)

ðŸ”§ Non-Functional Requirements
- Responsive design (mobile-first)
- Secure authentication & data encryption
- Scalability to support high traffic
- Reliable uptime (cloud-hosted, e.g., AWS, Firebase)
- Performance optimization (fast load times)
- Analytics & logging

ðŸŒŸ Optional/Advanced Features
- AI-based suggestions (e.g., best time/date, vendors)
- Vendor marketplace (caterers, DJs, photographers)
- Mood/theme templates
- Offline access
- Social sharing (Instagram, Facebook)
- Integration with calendars (Google Calendar, Outlook)
- Augmented reality previews (for venues, decor)
